## 空状态设计

搜索无结果时展示：

```vue
<div class="empty-state">
  <span class="empty-icon">🔍</span>
  <p>没有找到「{{ query }}」相关的回复</p>
  <button @click="goAdmin">去添加</button>
</div>
```

```css
.empty-state {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 48px 24px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  gap: 8px;
}
.empty-icon { font-size: 32px; }
```

